How To Learn Communication Skill:

* Verbal Communication: Recordings, Literature Review, Tutorials, Videos, Documentaries.Yeh method ko follow krke improve krskte hai.
* Vocabulary Devlopemet: Alfaazon ka zakheera apne mind mein jitni solid hugi ap ki communication utni behtar hugi.(Verbal bhi written bhi)
* Body Language: Like client ke saath meeting mein ap gusse wala face ya ap sochne wala face bnarahay hai,toh yeh matter hi nahi krega kay apki english kitni achi hai ,result bohat clear hai,isse kuch nahi pata .He is totally confused.
