* Non-Verbal Communication: Apke samne jab bhi client aaye smile gesture dein ,eye contact krein,hand movements zyada ya kam nahi hone chahiye.
* Written Communication: Bohat se tools hai market mein Grammmarly hai ap khud apne baaray mein ksi bhi topic pr likhein ,apko idea huga ap ke mind mein vocabulary kitni install hai,message likhein ,email likhein,articles,blog likhein.
* Visual Communication: Yeh cheeezain dikha kr smjhate hain ,yeh with the passage of time apko khud bakhud aajayegi.
* Listening Communication: Yeh sbse important hai kay ap ek 10 minute ki video focus hokar dekhein ap yeh gaur krein kay 10 minute ki video meinn apka focus kitni baar out huta hai ,agar focus 3 baar out huta hai toh ap yeh koshish krien kay ab focus 2 baar out ho.Phir aesa kray kay apka dhyaan ek baar bhi na hatay.Focu krne ki practice krni hai.Videos, Lectures, Tutorials, Webinars, Podcast dekhein, News Channel dekhein, cricket commentary and so other things